<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\string\strlen">strlen</sample>
    <title>strlen, wcslen</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> str_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>获得字符串的长度。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>size_t</return_val>
        <func_name>strlen</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>const char*</param_type>
                <param_name>string</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>以NULL结尾的字符串</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>size_t</return_val>
        <func_name>wcslen</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>const wchar_t*</param_type>
                <param_name>string</param_name>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>返回字符串中字符的个数，不包括结束符NULL。如无返回值则指示错误。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>两个函数都返回字符串中字符的个数，不包括结束符NULL。wcslen是strlen的宽字符版本，wcslen的参数是宽字符串。除此之外，与函数strlen一样。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>strlen</routine_name>
            <headerfile>string.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>wcslen</routine_name>
            <headerfile>string.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2008,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* strlen.cpp:this program use strlength to get the length of string
 */

#include &lt;string.h&gt;
#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;

int main()
{
    char buffer[61] = &quot;How long am I?&quot;;
    int  len;
    len = strlen(buffer);
    printf(&quot;&apos;%s&apos; is %d characters long\n&quot;, buffer, len);

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
&apos;How long am I?&apos; is 14 characters long
</result>



